		{
			"type": "action",
			"name": "Limithed Telepathy",
			"system": {
				"actionType": {
					"value": "action"
				},
				"description": {
					"value": "<p>The abyss swarm attempt to partially control the mind of a creature inside the swarm's space. Target creature must attempt at a @Check[will|dc:15] save. A creature can end the swarm's mind control with a @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.9HpwDN4MYQJnW0LG], @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.b515AZlB0sridKSq] or similar spells.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected and immune for 24 hours.</p><p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p><p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.yblD8fOR1J8rDwEQ]{Confused} for 1 round, and can't target the swarm.</p><p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> as failure, but the creature is confused for 1 minute.</p>",
